headline: In the Grip of Nature’s Own Form of Birth Control
snippet: You get obsessively vigilant when you realize having a baby is not just up to you.

headline: National Briefing | Washington: Blood-Clot Warning On Birth-Control Patch
snippet: Women were warned that their risk of blood clots in the legs and lungs may be higher if they use the birth-control patch instead of the pill.

headline: Clot Risk for Birth-Control Patch Is Found to Be Double That of Pill
snippet: A new study shows that women using the Ortho Evra birth-control patch have double the risk of developing blood clots compared with those who take the birth-control pill, the Food and Drug Administration said Friday.     But the agency called the...
